04:08.680 --> 04:11.920
We don't treat the trauma, we get rid
of it.

04:12.480 --> 04:13.880
You get rid of it?

04:15.120 --> 04:16.960
- Is it safe?
- Yes.

04:16.960 --> 04:21.880
