04:36.360 --> 04:39.160
Why is it always about the
money with you Charlton?

04:39.840 --> 04:41.480
Because I don't have any.

04:42.560 --> 04:44.360
- I'll speak to Rudy.
- No, no.

04:44.360 --> 04:45.760
