and you're going to come home.

09:27.800 --> 09:30.960
- It's hell.
- It's time. You're upsetting her.

09:37.840 --> 09:40.360
- I have to go. Okay?
- No.

09:42.120 --> 09:45.760
You bleed from your eyes, your ears.

09:49.400 --> 09:51.040
- Okay.
- No

09:52.520 --> 09:55.200
I'll come back. Okay?
I promise. I'll come back.

09:55.200 --> 09:57.000
