11:00.000 --> 11:02.080
Oh. I'm fine.

11:03.600 --> 11:04.760
I'm fine.

11:05.040 --> 11:06.280
Okay.

11:28.880 --> 11:30.480
Hi.

11:32.040 --> 11:33.400
Yola.

11:35.800 --> 11:37.240
It's so good to see you.

11:51.480 --> 11:53.920
- Sienna told me about...
